S --> NP: (^ SUBJ)=!
      VP: ^=!
          (^ SUBJ NUM)=(^ NUM)
          (^ SUBJ GEND)=(^ GEND).

VP --> V: ^=!
       (NP: (^ OBJ)=!)
       (PP: (^ OBL-AG)=!)
       (PP*: !$ (^ ADJUNCT)).

NP --> (D: (^ DEF)=+)
       N: ^=!
       (PP*: !$ (^ ADJUNCT)).

PP --> P: ^=!
       { NP: (^ OBJ)=!
       | N:  (^ OBJ)=!
             (^ OBJ DEF)=+ }.